com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core
Interface FShapeM

All Superinterfaces:
FShape, java.io.Serializable, java.awt.Shape
All Known Implementing Classes:
FPoint2DM, FPolygon2DM, FPolyline2DM, FPolyline3DM
public interface FShapeM
extends FShape

This interface has to be implemented by all the shapes that has a M value in its nodes. It will be possible to manage the M coordinate for every node.

Author:
Jorge Piera LLodrá (jorge.piera@iver.es)
